### 1. Create a New Product (Ganti categoryId dengan id category yang ada)
POST http://localhost:4015/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 1,
  "name": "Sourdough Bread",
  "description": "Freshly baked artisan sourdough bread",
  "price": 45000,
  "type": "DAILY_BAKE",
  "stock": 20
}

### 2. Get All Products
GET http://localhost:4015/api/products

### 3. Get Product by ID (Ganti ID sesuai dengan hasil create)
GET http://localhost:4015/api/products/1

### 4. Update Product (Ganti ID sesuai kebutuhan)
PATCH http://localhost:4015/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Artisan Sourdough Bread",
  "price": 48000,
  "stock": 15
}

### 5. Delete Product (Ganti ID sesuai kebutuhan)
DELETE http://localhost:4015/api/products/1
